description_html: This contemporary outdoor furniture set is made from durable, all-weather HDPE wicker that's been hand-woven around a tubular aluminum frame. The Novel 6 Piece Set also includes acrylic Sunbrella® seat, back and bolster cushions that are fade- and mildew-resistant. Cushions are removable and have removable covers that make cleaning your patio set a breeze. The Novel outdoor seating set by Stori Modern includes 2 outdoor lounge chairs, 2 outdoor ottomans, 1 outdoor love seat and 1 outdoor coffee table. Available colors include coffee, beige and white.
